survey.music_making: Self taught guitar, drums, bass starting at age 10. Rock/indie influences. Played saxophone in high school band for 4 years. Played in gospel groups at churches (drums) age 10-13. Played in various local rock groups during ages 15-27.
survey.activities: Playing online games, driving, exercising, laundry, cleaning
survey.habit_change: I would say I listen to a wider variety of music and usually prefer sounds that are less heavy.
survey.habits: I usually find a artist I like and listen to them for a while. I sometimes have songs that I will always play first when starting a listening session.
